      <title>法院裁决前总理伊姆兰·汗泄露秘密电报伤害了巴基斯坦</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ex-pm-imran-khans-leak-secret-cable-hurt-pakistan-court-ruling-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 泄露一份秘密外交电报，对这个南亚国家的经济、政治和外交造成了损害，法庭在周四做出有罪判决并判处他 10 年监禁后发布了详细的判决书。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ex-pm-imran-khans-leak-secret-cable-hurt-pakistan-court-ruling-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：以色列袭击后伊朗卫队从叙利亚撤回军官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-guards-pull-officers-syria-after-israeli-strikes-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五位知情人士称，由于以色列发动一系列致命袭击，伊朗革命卫队已缩减了在叙利亚的高级军官部署，并将更多地依靠什叶派民兵盟军来维持其在叙利亚的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-guards-pull-officers-syria-after-israeli-strikes-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾选出议会议长执政党观点亲中</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾议会周四选举最大反对党的前总统候选人为新议长，他将负责接待来访的外国议员，执政党称他是亲中国的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:26:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯议员称朝鲜代表团将访问莫斯科</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-delegation-visit-moscow-russian-lawmaker-says-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方通讯社俄新社周四援引反对党共产党一名代表的话说，朝鲜代表团将于 2 月 13 日访问俄罗斯议会下院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-delegation-visit-moscow-russian-lawmaker-says-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港亿万富翁李泽楷寻求出售资产管理公司 PineBridge - 消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-billionaire-richard-li-seeks-sell-asset-manager-pinebridge-sources-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三名知情人士和路透社看到的交易文件透露，由亿万富翁李泽楷创立的香港投资公司盈科拓展集团（PCG）正在寻求出售其在资产管理公司柏瑞投资（PineBridge Investments）的多数股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-billionaire-richard-li-seeks-sell-asset-manager-pinebridge-sources-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:43:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚领导人被指控存在偏见并干涉总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-leader-accused-bias-interference-presidential-election-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚总统佐科·维多多在本月总统选举中竞选主要候选人时，因被视为政治干预和缺乏中立性而面临越来越多的公众批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-leader-accused-bias-interference-presidential-election-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼市场因选举不确定性和金融业的未来而动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesian-markets-rattled-by-election-uncertainty-finmins-future-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一段相对平静的时期后，印度尼西亚市场显示出对旷日持久的全国大选前景以及该国备受尊敬的财政部长斯里·穆利亚尼·英德拉瓦蒂(Sri Mulyani Indrawati)离职的可能性的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesian-markets-rattled-by-election-uncertainty-finmins-future-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:15:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师提出解散申请，泰国大选获胜者面临新打击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-blow-thai-election-winners-lawyer-launches-dissolution-bid-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名激进律师周四提交请愿书，寻求解散泰国前进党，因为该党计划修改一项保护君主制免受批评的法律，这对于一个以大胆的自由改革议程赢得选举的政党来说是一次挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-blow-thai-election-winners-lawyer-launches-dissolution-bid-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SK海力士将在印第安纳州建造先进工厂，以促进美国芯片自给自足 - FT</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/sk-hynix-build-advanced-plant-indiana-boost-us-chip-self-sufficiency-ft-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》周四报道，韩国芯片制造商 SK 海力士已选择在美国印第安纳州建立尖端工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/sk-hynix-build-advanced-plant-indiana-boost-us-chip-self-sufficiency-ft-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划购买潜艇以捍卫南海主权——高级官员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-plans-buy-submarines-defend-sovereignty-south-china-sea-senior-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯已批准军队现代化的第三阶段，其中包括购买该国第一艘潜艇，以捍卫其在有争议的南中国海的海洋主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-plans-buy-submarines-defend-sovereignty-south-china-sea-senior-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
